cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.IR, cs.CL 

The paper focuses on organ annotation in medical images, which is a task related to computer vision (cs.CV). The paper also introduces a reasoning framework based on learning fuzzy relations, which is a topic related to artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and machine learning (cs.LG). The use of constraints for solving the organ annotation task is also related to information retrieval (cs.IR) and natural language processing (cs.CL).
